
<html tal:omit-tag=""
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      i18n:domain="ideabox.policy">
<tal:comment tal:replace="nothing">
    A lot of javascript relies on classes and structure to be present. Before
    changing anything, please check that twothumbs.js isn't expecting it.
</tal:comment>

<div tal:omit-tag="" i18n:translate="">
    <span i18n:name="login" tal:omit-tag="">
        <a class="link-overlay"
           tal:attributes="href string:${context/portal_url}/login_form?came_from=${request/HTTP_REFERER}"
           i18n:translate="">Log in to rate</a>
    </span>
    <a i18n:name="close-link" i18n:attributes="title" title="Close" class="close-link" style="display:block;" href="#">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
</html>
